snippet.title: Lloyd the Monkey 3: Judgement Day - SAGE 2022 Trailer #Lloyd3
snippet.description:
SAGE is practically here, and so is the first Lloyd the Monkey 3 demo! We've prepared a trailer for people still on the fence to view before trying the game out, while also providing a peek at the game's storyline. Enjoy the trailer and the demo.

Subscribe to Patreon.com/MeyerGames for advance updates on the game's development and future Lloyd the Monkey content. Perks begin as little as $1.

Music: Beautiful Cruel World (from Attack on Titan S1, English Ver. by @LeeandLie 
Voice Actors: @meyergames  @HALchannel108
